00:42:24,697 --> 00:42:29,423
In the center is that black spot, which is representative of this nirodha.

395
00:42:29,443 --> 00:42:35,112
And then there's the bright white light of pure awareness.

396
00:42:35,653 --> 00:42:37,996
And then, of course, the manifestation into the world

397
00:42:41,538 --> 00:42:43,501
So, yeah, that's it really.

398
00:42:43,902 --> 00:42:50,552
And then, of course, he gives us the practice to be able to attain that.

399
00:42:50,672 --> 00:42:56,282
So it's sort of a fabulous, a fabulous legacy that he's left the world, you know, the Buddha.

400
00:43:00,489 --> 00:43:03,574
I think I'm drying up now.

401
00:43:03,594 --> 00:43:04,677
It's really what time it is.

402
00:43:05,057 --> 00:43:05,318
How are you?

403
00:43:08,217 --> 00:43:09,159
Good heavens, I have done it.

404
00:43:09,179 --> 00:43:10,581
I've done 40 minutes, haven't I?

405
00:43:10,601 --> 00:43:11,802
I have actually, I've made it.

406
00:43:12,425 --> 00:43:13,527
That's it.

407
00:43:16,851 --> 00:43:19,376
I can only hope my words have been of some assistance.

408
00:43:19,396 --> 00:43:21,581
They have not caused greater confusion.

409
00:43:21,601 --> 00:43:28,512
And that you will, by your efforts, liberate yourself from all suffering.

410
00:43:28,833 --> 00:43:29,414
Thank you.

